      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the marque, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a meticulously serviced double-VANOS system. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides precise, tactile gear engagement, delivering power to the rear wheels via the variable M Differential Lock. The chassis is structurally pristine, with the rear subframe mounting points fully inspected and reinforced for long-term durability. All suspension components maintain factory-correct geometry, and the braking system features cross-drilled rotors with optimal clamping force. This vehicle has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showing zero signs of thermal cycling wear on gaskets or seals. It is a mechanically flawless, collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
